'''Prostitot''' is a derogatory term for [[America]]n prepubescent girls who dress to emulate the dress styles and attitudes of [[twenty something]] women such as [[Britney Spears]]. It especially means those who wear tight jeans and bare belly shirts. The age category is generally consideered to be 10 to 14 year olds. Also included are form fitting short shirts, miniskirts and heavy makeup.

See also:[[Poptart]] [[Jailbait]] and [[kinderwhore]]

